---
title: Peruvian Inspired Sea Bream and Zingy King Prawns with Sweet Potato Slices and Charred Corn & Avocado Salsa
description: With its long coastline, Peru is home to many sensational seafood dishes. Discover the vibrant flavours of Peruvian staples such as chillies, limes, coriander and corn in this dish for a colourful meal that brings the sun and sea of Peru with it.
